OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry evening,
OL,6,Fbefore thicker cloud spreads south.
OL,7,FMost parts staying dry, but this could
OL,8,Fbring some brief light rain. Further
OL,9,Fclear spells follow later, but winds
OL,10,Falso strengthening slightly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FVariable cloud but also some
OL,13,Fsunny spells initially with cloud and
OL,14,Fshowers arriving through the morning.
OL,15,FThese will clear through the afternoon
OL,16,Fleaving drier and brighter conditions.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
