OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers Sunday, these
OL,7,Fperhaps heavy at times. Drier Monday,
OL,8,Fwith variable cloud and sunny spells.
OL,9,FCloudier and breezier Tuesday, with
OL,10,Frain across hills. Temperatures near
OL,11,Fnormal.
